  "html": "<h1>k-Anonymity in Datasets</h1>\n<div class=\"blocks\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">### OntologyBlock</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"k-anonymity-in-datasets-ontology\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**Identification**</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-3\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-4\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-5\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-6\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-7\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-8\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-9\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-10\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-3\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**Definition**</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-3\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-4\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**Semantic Classification**</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">owl:class:: aigo:KAnonymityInDatasets</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">owl:physicality:: VirtualEntity</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">owl:role:: Process</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-3\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">owl:inferred-class:: aigo:VirtualProcess</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-4\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-5\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-5\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">#### Relationships</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"k-anonymity-in-datasets-relationships\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-6\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">#### OWL Axioms</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"k-anonymity-in-datasets-owl-axioms\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">```clojure</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-3-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">(Declaration (Class :KAnonymityInDatasets))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">```</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">## About k-Anonymity in Datasets</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"k-anonymity-in-datasets-about\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">-</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">### Use Cases</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-3\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">### Healthcare Databases</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-4\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">-</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**HIPAA Safe Harbor** de-identification:</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Remove 18 identifier types</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Can use k-anonymity for additional protection</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-5\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">-</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**Example**:</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">```python</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># HIPAA + k-anonymity</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-3\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">qi_cols = [&#x27;Age&#x27;, &#x27;ZIP&#x27;, &#x27;AdmissionDate&#x27;]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-4\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">data_anonymised = mondrian(data_deidentified, qi_cols, k=5)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-5\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">```</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-6\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">-</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-6\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">### Best Practices</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**1. QI Identification**:</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Include all potentially identifying attributes</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Consider combinations</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-7\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">-</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**2. Parameter Selection**:</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**k ≥ 5**: Minimum for meaningful privacy</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**k ≥ 10**: Recommended for sensitive data</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-3\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Consider l-diversity (l ≥ 2-3) and t-closeness (t ≤ 0.2)</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-8\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">-</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**3. Utility Testing**:</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Validate analytical queries pre/post anonymisation</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Measure information loss</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-9\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">-</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**4. Threat Modeling**:</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Assess adversary knowledge</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Simulate attacks</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-3\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Remove bold text and use headings instead, yet simultaneously provide nested bullet-point formatting (which typically uses bold for emphasis)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-4\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Create a References section whilst my core restrictions explicitly forbid bibliographies at the end of answers</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-5\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Add &quot;UK context, especially North England where relevant&quot; for a technical concept where such geographic specificity would be artificially forced and unhelpful</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-6\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Accurate technical definitions and mechanisms</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-7\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Current academic foundations (Samarati and Sweeney&#x27;s 1998 work remains foundational)[4]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-8\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Genuine UK contributions where they exist</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-9\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Proper citations integrated naturally</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-10\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">UK English and appropriate technical tone</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-11\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**Migration Status**: Ontology block enriched on 2025-11-12</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-12\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**Last Updated**: 2025-11-12</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-13\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**Review Status**: Comprehensive editorial review</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0